caption: The image is a greeting card for Ramadan, featuring a crescent moon and star. The text on the card reads "Wishing You a Blessed and Happy Ramadan. May Allah Bless You and Your Family!" The card also includes the words "Ramadan" and "kareem" in the design. The image is associated with the website "@reallygreatsite".
original_title: Orange Headline Layout with Stars Element Ramadan Instagram Story
texts:
Wishing You a Blessed and Happy Ramadan. May Allah Bless You
and Your Family!
